The station was inaugurated in August 1908 by a German association, Anatolia-Baghdad Corporation.
Germany, which is lagging behind in the game of imperialism, wanted to achieve its medieval ambitions of domination thanks to this railway which arrives in Damascus, Baghdad as well as the land better known as Saudi Arabia.
